name: GreetingDialogue
Start
Nagatoro says Hello, welcome to Nagatoro Novel Game!
Player says Hi Nagatoro, nice to meet you!
Nagatoro says How are you doing today?
set playerScore = 0
set playerName = "New Player"
Jump To SecondScene
End

---

name: SecondScene
Start
Player says This is the second scene.
If Show Variant
Variants:
Option A
Option B
True:
Print You chose option A
False:
Print You chose option B
endif
End

function greetPlayer
Wait 2 seconds
Player says Hello everyone!
Nagatoro says Nice to see you again!
Player says See you next time!
end

call greetPlayer